headline: Household Products Stocks Q1 Results: Benchmarking Clorox (NYSE:CLX)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q1. Today, we are looking at household products stocks, starting with Clorox (NYSE:CLX).
